item.title: Help on typin an essay on harry potter and half blood prince
item.dc:creator: @goatee goatee
item.description:
@goatee wrote:

Talk about what the book continues from… like a very small summary of the last book and where it is now. Then write down notes on all the main events. Focus on characters and how they are changing. The relationships of characters. Try to comment on that during every main event. Of couse you can use that guide for almost any book but i think it helps.

PS: For a conclusion write about how the book ends and where you thinks its going to lead to in the next book.
